,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:38:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教畜<br />\n入行嗰堆都係為咗兩萬幾起薪點<br />\n教員室入面嘅政治要幾醜惡有幾醜惡<br />\n仲要周不時周爐講細路家長壞話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個人最睇唔過眼係教畜呃細路仔感情<br />\n<br />\n記得好耐以前，讀緊小學個時，有個老師成日都會話最錫等地，對比其他班對我地最好，比d優越感我地，等我地聽佢話d,個時已經心諗個個。你都咁講嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家諗番真係痴撚線，對住小學生都要宮心計咁"},{"pid":"420d105d68a0fa6aafcf85845cb55e25843c7ffe","tid":219303,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:38:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解冇人講大陸官員/公務員，為人民服務喎，聽到都想嘔</blockquote><br />\n個Post都係啱啱開姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4767aa7eb032199834a51549bb6c2ead418b28","tid":219303,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老師邊到係呀屌<br />\n<br />\n大把人為左份高薪9衝囉<br />\n<br />\n咁點算偽善</blockquote><br />\n問題係有啲工種係有一份社會責任<br />\n甚至係因為社會責任而高薪<br />\n所以先有警犬教畜呢啲term<br />\n就係形容呢啲𢭃住高人工<br />\n而又有負於社會期望嘅人<br />\n其他工種只要你唔係入錯油炸爆咗隻油船嘅話<br />\n其實對個社會影響不大"},{"pid":"25c92a3d0b1050b20c7a909a64259c8c5fa7718c","tid":219303,"uid":69302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:43:55.000Z","msg":"係連登講職業 都無咩邊行唔比人屌/狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36993dc259723b71ad71d83d521d039b8eabc58f","tid":219303,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:45:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係連登講職業 都無咩邊行唔比人屌/狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n消防？老柳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /